  m_text: '- It is one of the most popular programming language in the world


    -
    If you know <color=green>C<color=white>, you will have no problem learning other
    popular programming languages such as <color=green>Java<color=white>, <color=green>Python<color=white>,
    <color=green>C++<color=white>, <color=green>C#<color=white>, etc, as the syntax
    is similar


    - <color=green>C<color=white> is very fast, compared to other
    programming languages, like Java and Python'
